                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 0.0161em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">问：为什么 </span><span class="stl_26 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">PLC </span><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">设备通过 </span><span class="stl_26 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">USB </span><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0121em;">连接在智能远程模块管理后台看不见设备？ &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 1.8161em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_27 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0127em;">答：这是因为电脑没有安装 </span><span class="stl_29 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0127em;">USB </span><span class="stl_27 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0127em;">驱动程序导致的，具体操作如下： &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 3.6161em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_09">※</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 3.6161em; left:8.067em;"><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_09">第一步：准备好</span><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0005em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_26 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0005em;">USB</span><span class="stl_26 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0244em;">&nbsp;</span><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0244em;">驱动程序（通过下载或者找到现成的驱动程序）</span><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0244em;">&nbsp;。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 5.4161em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_09">※</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 5.4161em; left:8.0678em;"><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_32">第二步：右键点击</span><span class="stl_26 stl_08 stl_32">“</span><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_32">我的电脑</span><span class="stl_26 stl_08 stl_32">”</span><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_32">，然后左键点击</span><span class="stl_26 stl_08 stl_32">“</span><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_32">管理</span><span class="stl_26 stl_08 stl_32">&gt;</span><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_32">设备管理器</span><span class="stl_26 stl_08 stl_32">”</span><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_32">，在</span><span class="stl_26 stl_08 stl_32">“</span><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_32">其他设备</span><span class="stl_26 stl_08 stl_32">”</span><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_32">点开树形图，找 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 6.7161em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0003em;">到 </span><span class="stl_26 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0003em;">USB Device</span><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_09" style="word-spacing:-0.0003em;">。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 16.3161em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_09">※</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 16.3161em; left:8.067em;"><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_47" style="word-spacing:0.0156em;">第三步：右键点击 </span><span class="stl_26 stl_08 stl_47" style="word-spacing:0.0156em;">USB Device </span><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_47" style="word-spacing:0.0156em;">然后点击更新驱动程序选择从列表或指定位置安装（高级），并点 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 17.6161em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_25 stl_08 stl_09">击下一步，根据提示把驱动安装完成。 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 38.9161em; left:7.4833em;"><span class="stl_27 stl_08 stl_48" style="word-spacing:-0.0324em;">驱动安装成功后，</span><span class="stl_29 stl_08 stl_48" style="word-spacing:-0.0324em;">PLC </span><span class="stl_27 stl_08 stl_48" style="word-spacing:-0.0324em;">设备就能在管理后台看见了，此时在设备管理器里点开</span><span class="stl_29 stl_08 stl_48" style="word-spacing:-0.0324em;">“</span><span class="stl_27 stl_08 stl_48" style="word-spacing:-0.0324em;">通用串行总线控制 &nbsp;</span></div>
                    <div class="stl_01" style="top: 40.2161em; left:5.7333em;"><span class="stl_27 stl_08 stl_09">器”的树形图显示如下图： &nbsp;</span></div>
